{"tid":1661282,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人參選諾貝爾和平獎   外交部：挪威停止干預香港事務","createTime":"2019-10-18T04:15:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T10:50:16.000Z","uid":65371,"like":56,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"f7da44cafcf73f4b7f9fe01bc3155cebeaf6137d","tid":1661282,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:15:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/393304404377707/posts/970408953333913/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F393304404377707%2Fposts%2F970408953333913%2F&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=59455995\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/393304404377707/posts/970408953333913/</a><br />\n<br />\n【挪威議員提名「香港人」參選諾貝爾和平獎 外交部敦促有關人士謹言慎行，停止以任何形式干預香港事務】<br />\n<br />\n在昨日外交部例行記者會上，有記者問，一名挪威政客提名全體香港人參與2020年諾貝爾和平獎競選，中方對此有何評論？<br />\n<br />\n發言人耿爽表示，香港事務純屬中國內政，任何外國政府、組織和個人都無權干涉。我們敦促有關人士本著客觀、公正的態度，謹言慎行，停止以任何形式干預香港事務、干涉中國內政。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/LXCA4XRpJblDTSoW8XTtHw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2FLXCA4XRpJblDTSoW8XTtHw&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=c84f02c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/LXCA4XRpJblDTSoW8XTtHw</a><br />\n<br />\n----------<br />\n<br />\n歡迎關注公署官方微信公眾號(帳號:fmcoprc)，希望為你提供豐富有益的資訊和便捷周到的服務。"},{"pid":"0bb8767f2ffd49a7021759a0be4db4f6964ba6c5","tid":1661282,"uid":3405,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:16:07.000Z","msg":"耿不爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cbd7e220594ff6be076a3729695b0689ed33e10","tid":1661282,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:17:29.000Z","msg":"【FC】西九站遊行係中共真春袋！<span style=\"color: red;\">需要針對強國文宣<strong>輸出革命</strong></span>！<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>消息人士表示，7月7日過10萬人去到高鐵西九龍站後，「中國國家安全委員會」就對西九龍站「突發」事件設定了「專案」，就各種事況的發生計劃了處理辦法。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1661232\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1661232</a>"},{"pid":"19503aa1b1966f8485f291bfdb0fd6a5043278f4","tid":1661282,"uid":57659,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:17:30.000Z","msg":"俾獎你都叫干預你<br />\n同你做生意唔通就係打劫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f0daae6c415677c30c7ce547ae47598919086b","tid":1661282,"uid":300006,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:19:13.000Z","msg":"佢叫人地唔好做既同時都干預緊人地既內政<br />\n共慘黨唔好咁豬腦啦，啊寶無得抖會死架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b22043394d8dd4d2f23089e32a058329b12789","tid":1661282,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:19:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">𨳒你老母中共外交部</span>"},{"pid":"696670a5ad1e0e44464de2c86714c6535655fd78","tid":1661282,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:19:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"638eca4d8ebc9d4749d7d8d4a9a7c3d1970a06bb","tid":1661282,"uid":65371,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:20:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YgG2oH7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYgG2oH7.jpg&h=51305427&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34431dc7fffcfcc0374491eac31e7fbed8171339","tid":1661282,"uid":334806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"638eca4d8ebc9d4749d7d8d4a9a7c3d1970a06bb","tid":1661282,"uid":65371,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:20:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YgG2oH7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYgG2oH7.jpg&h=51305427&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-1